Package Player

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Mp3
    Mp3 container class, this fetches and makes easily accessible all the metadata contained in the Mp3 or, if not present, sets default properties.
    MusicHandler
    MusicHandler class, this launches and controls a thread that acts as the main music player.
    MusicLibrary
    Music Library class, contains an array of Mp3 objects.
    MusicPlayerFrame
    Main interface class, this constructs and runs everything in the main window.
    NanoHTTPD
    A simple, tiny, nicely embeddable HTTP 1.0 (partially 1.1) server in Java
    WebServer
    Subclassing NanoHTTPD to make a custom HTTP server.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MusicHandler.STATE
    Enumeration of the current state of the player.
